'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da cewa za a kwatanta su da Muppets
Akwai tashin hankali a tsakanin 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales game da wani batu da ya sa aka canja sunayensu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament - 'Yan majalisar Wales).
Wannan shawarar ta biyo bayan shirin sauya sunan yanzu na 'Welsh Assembly' zuwa 'Welsh Parliament'.
'Yan majalisar dokokin kasar na jam'iyyun siyasa daban-daban sun damu da cewa sabon sunan zai zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisar dokokin Wales na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce MWP ta yi amfani da TPP da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: twp shi ne Welsh don mahaukaci da pwp shi ne Welsh don shit.
Wani dan majalisar dokokin Wales na jam'iyyar Plaid ya ce kungiyar a matsayin cikakkiyar ba ta gamsu da shi ba kuma ya gabatar da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Welsh Conservative Party ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta yi murabus da sauya sunansa, amma ya lura cewa kalmomin MWP da Muppet sun yi kama da juna.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta haruffan Welsh W a matsayin ɗan gajeren u.
Kwamitin Majalisar Dokokin Wales, wanda ke aiki a yanzu wajen tsara dokokin da za su sa a canja sunan, ya ce: Littafin Majalisar Dokokin Wales ne ke yanke shawara game da sabon taken su.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales damar canza sunan majalisar.
