Peter Jones "ya yi fushi" bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Peter Jones, daya daga cikin taurari na Dragon's Den, yana da "zafin rai" saboda mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 da kamfanin rayuwarsa.
Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don Truly, alamarsu ta kayan gida da kayan haɗi.
Wani lokaci ana kwatanta kamfanin Jones da Willoughby da alamar Gwyneth Paltrow ta Goop.
