Peter Jones na Dragon's Den ya fusata da Holly Willoughby, saboda a lokacin ƙarshe ta janye daga kamfanin rayuwarsu mai riba don mayar da hankali kan kwangila da ta yi da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ya yi fushi lokacin da Willoughby ya sanar a wani taro mai wuya a hedkwatar kamfanin a Marlow, Buckinghamshire a ranar Talata cewa saboda sababbin kwangila (da suka kai kimanin fam miliyan daya da rabi) ba ta da isasshen lokaci don Truly, alamarsu ta kayan gida da kayan haɗi.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow ta Goop kuma ana sa ran zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby da aka kiyasta a £11m.
A lokacin da Willoughby mai shekara 37 ta sanar a shafinta na Instagram cewa za ta bar Truly, Jones ya tafi daya daga cikin gidajen hutu a kasashen waje.
Wata majiya ta ce, "Truly na ɗaya daga cikin manyan abubuwan da Holly ke so.
