Daruruwan Mutane Sun Mutu Saboda Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia, Kuma Yawan Mutane Yana Ƙaruwa
A ranar Asabar, jami'ai sun ce, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia sun kashe mutane akalla 384, inda aka shafe ƙasa da yawa sa'ad da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka rushe a bakin rairayin bakin teku.
A ranar Juma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin bakin teku a birnin Palu, sa'ad da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi na mita shida suka sauka a lokacin da aka fara duhu, mutane da yawa suka yi ta rushewa kuma raƙuman ruwa sun halaka duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu.
Tsunami ya faru ne sakamakon girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 a sikelin Richter.
"Sa'ad da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami a jiya, har yanzu akwai mutane a bakin rairayin bakin teku, ba su gudu ba, kuma sun zama wadanda suka sha wahala daga tsunami", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin hukumar kula da bala'in yanayi ta BNPB a Jakarta a wani taron da aka yi.
"Tsunami ya haifar da wasu haɗari: ya jawo motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya taɓa komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugroho, wanda ya ƙara da cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya da sauri a cikin teku mai gudu da kilomita 800 a kowace awa kafin ya kai ga gabar teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane suna hawa cikin itace don su tsira daga tsunami.
An kwashe mutane 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a Palu.
Hotunan da hukumar agaji ta fitar a sama sun nuna cewa gine-gine da shaguna da yawa sun lalace, gadoji sun karye kuma sun rushe, kuma ana kewaye da masallaci da ruwa.
A ranar Asabar, an ci gaba da girgiza garin da ke bakin tekun saboda girgizar ƙasa.
An ji jerin girgizar ƙasa a wani yanki da ke da mazaunan mutane miliyan biyu da dubu hudu da dubu hudu.
Hukumar tantancewa da kuma amfani da fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce, wutar da aka fitar a lokacin girgizar ƙasa mai girma da ta auku a ranar Juma'a, ta ninka na atomatik da aka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu a Hiroshima sau 200.
Ya ce, yanayin garin da ke kan gaɓar wani gajeren gaɓar teku mai tsawo zai iya ƙara daɗa tsunami.
Nugroho ya bayyana cewa an yi mummunan lalacewa kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da kuma otal-otal sun rushe.
Ya ce wasu cikin wadanda suka mutu sun makale a karkashin rushewar gine-gine, inda mutane 540 suka ji rauni kuma 29 sun bace.
Nugroho ya ce yawan mutanen da suka mutu da kuma lalacewar da ta faru sun fi girma a bakin tekun da ke da nisan mil 300 daga arewacin Palu, a wani yanki da ake kira Donggala, wanda ke kusa da inda girgizar ta auku.
A cewar Nugroho, sadarwa da Donggala ba ta da kyau.
