Kanye West: Rapper ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye
Rapper Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
A ranar Asabar da ta gabata, ya sanar da canjin a shafinsa na Twitter, yana cewa: "Wanda aka sani da sunan Kanye West".
West mai shekara 41 da haihuwa, wanda aka yi masa lakabi da Ye na ɗan lokaci, ya yi amfani da wannan sunan a matsayin taken littafinsa na takwas, wanda aka fitar a watan Yuni.
An sanar da canjin sunan ne a gabanin wasan kwaikwayonsa a ranar Asabar da dare Live, inda ake tsammanin zai gabatar da sabon kundin Yandhi.
Ya maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wadda ta soke aikinta a lokacin wasan saboda "abubuwan motsin rai", in ji mai gabatar da wasan.
Ba wai kawai gajeren sunan da West yake amfani da shi ba ne, amma ya riga ya gaya masa cewa kalmar tana da ma'ana ta addini.
A ganina, ye ita ce kalmar da ta fi kowa a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki, kuma a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki tana nufin jij, West ya ce a farkon wannan shekara, sa'ad da yake magana game da taken kundi a gaban mai gabatar da rediyo Big Boy.
"Saboda haka ni ne kai, ni ne mu, mu ne".
Na sauya daga Kanye, wanda ke nufin "kawai" zuwa "Y", wanda ke nuna nagarta a cikinmu, mugunta, rikicewa, komai.
Wannan kundin ya nuna ainihin yadda muke.
Ba shi ne kawai shahararren rapper da ya canza sunansa ba.
Sean Combs da aka sani da sunan Puff Daddy, P. Diddy ko Diddy, amma a wannan shekara ya sanar da fifiko ga sunayen Love da Brother Love.
Jay-Z, wanda ya yi aiki tare da West, ya yi aiki tare da kuma ba tare da alamar da manyan haruffa ba.
