Lokaci na taron zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron kara-karya a Wheeling, West Virginia a yau.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan da Trump ke shirin yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wuraren da yake so, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka dakatar da zaben dan takarar da ya zaɓa don zama a Kotun Koli, Trump yana son ya tara tallafi don zaɓen tsakiya mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na cikin haɗarin rasa iko a kan Majalisar Dokoki lokacin da aka yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai fara a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma yaya kuke kallon layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, zai fara ne a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe 19.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh a wannan makon, wanda ya kara da cewa an zargi Kavanaugh da aikata lalata ta jima'i, kuma a wataƙila Majalisar Dattawa za ta jira mako guda don amincewa da nadin sa yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman neman zaben a watan Nuwamba su kara samun karfin gwiwa.
Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan gangamin biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, suna da nufin karfafa masu sa kai da magoya bayan su, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
Sarrafawa a kan majalisa yana da mahimmanci ga shirinsa, cewa shugaban yana tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu a lokacin da kakar yakin neman zabe ta fara, wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ya shaida wa Reuters.
Taron da za a yi a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling a yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya yi magana a cikin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ce.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican na majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya rage a zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi damar yin zabe", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
