HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabon kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ce adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ce sun shafi mutane fiye da 820,000 a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane 40,000.
A yawancin sababbin cututtuka, ana iya samun cututtuka ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ba haka ba ne a dā.
A baya, cutar HIV ta yi sauri ta yaduwa a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar karban jini.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar yanzu ya kusan raguwa, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, idan aka kwatanta da wannan lokacin a bara, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
Tun daga shekarar 1997 ba a yi wa 'yan luwadi laifi a kasar Sin ba, amma an ce ana nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi.
Domin ra'ayin ƙasar da ya dace, an kiyasta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri wata mace.
Sau da yawa, ana iya samun cututtuka ta wajen rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin cutar HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
