Johnny English Strikes Again - wani ɗan leƙen asiri mai ban tsoro da Rowan Atkinson ya yi
A duk wani sabon fim da ke da tasirin Burtaniya, yanzu mun saba neman nassoshi na Brexit, kuma hakan ya bayyana a zahiri ya shafi wannan farfadowar da ke faruwa a cikin kyautar Johnny English, fim din wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo tare da wani ɗan leken asiri mai rauni, wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma aka sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin wannan baƙar magana game da yadda muke yin rashin lafiya ta zama sabon samfurin fitarwa ga ƙasarmu?
Johnny English, wanda ba shi da kwarewa, da idanunsa masu tsalle da kuma fuskarsa mai sauƙi, aƙalla yana iya yin kome a cikin ɗari, har ma da dawowarsa ta biyu. Da sunansa, za ka iya cewa shi mutum ne mai ban dariya da aka tsara don masu zuwa fina-finai a ƙasashen da ake magana da harshe dabam da Turanci.
Ya kasance, ba shakka, wani ɗan sanda ne mai zaman kansa wanda, duk da cewa yana da kyakkyawar ma'ana, yana da ɗan Clouseau, da ɗan Mr Bean da kuma ɗan ɗan ɗanɗano daga mutumin da ya ba da bayanin kula ɗaya ga lambar taken "Takarun wuta" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London a 2012.
An fara ne da wannan matafiyi da kuma mutumin da Atkinson ya yi wa'azi a duniya a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na talabijin na Barclaycard (wanda kowa ya manta da shi a yanzu) wanda koyaushe yana barin wani rikici.
Wani hoton da ya yi na Johnny English ya nuna wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da yadda Johnny English ya zo kusa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu a cikin makamai na ƙarni na farko, kuma ya yi ta ɗora takalman rotor a kan helmet.
Atkinson na iya nuna a cikin wannan fim yadda yake da basira ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma ba'a da kyau a nuna cewa ba'a da kyau kuma yana da ban dariya, musamman ma yanzu da jerin fina-finai masu tsanani kamar 007 da Mission Impossible sun hada da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki, kuma suna yin hakan da kyau.
Kuma ban da haka ma, ban da cewa ana son yara su yi ba, amma na fi son manya. Kuma munanan abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi a rayuwa ba su da kyau sosai, kuma ba su da ma'ana sosai fiye da ban dariya da ba su da rubutu na Bean da Atkinson ya buga.
Yanzu dai batun da ke ci gaba da kasancewa a nan shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo mai zurfin asiri, wanda ya bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an sirri da ke aiki a Birtaniya, wanda ya sa jami'in da ke aiki ya firgita, wanda ke da karamin rawar Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya sa Firayim Minista ya yi amfani da shi sosai, mace mai girman kai da ke da matsala a kai kuma ba ta da kyau a matsayin 'yar siyasa. Emma Thompson tana yin iyakar ƙoƙarinta don ta yi amfani da wannan halin da ke tuna da Teresa May, amma rubutun ba ya ba da kayan aiki da yawa don aiki tare da.
Masu ba ta shawara a fannin leken asiri sun ce ta bukaci ta tura wani ɗan leken asiri da ya yi ritaya, domin duk wani ɗan leken asiri da ke aiki an yi masa barazana.
Wannan yana nufin Johnny English da kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wata makarantar da ta fi dacewa amma yana koyar da darasi ba bisa hukuma ba game da aikin ɓoye.
An gayyaci English zuwa Whitehall don aikawa da wasiƙar gaggawa kuma an sake haɗa shi da tsohon mataimakinsa mai baƙin ciki Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, matarsa kuma ta zama kyaftin din jirgin ruwa, wani matsayi mai ban tsoro da kuma farin ciki wanda ya fi Vicki Pepperdine girma.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin na rundunar sirrin sarauta sun koma aiki kuma sun sadu da matar Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, ba shakka, Firayim Minista ya yi mamakin wani biliyan mai fasaha mai ban sha'awa wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta, mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun soma tafiyarsu ta farin ciki: sun yi ado da su kuma sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau, sun yi ta yin hayaniya a kan jirgin jirgin ruwa mai kayatarwa na Volta, kuma English ya jawo rashin jin daɗin gaske lokacin da ya yi ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar mai kwakwalwa ta Virtual Reality don ya san gidan Volta.
A lokacin da aka yi wannan aikin, an buɗe dukan littattafan da aka rubuta, amma duk da cewa an yi niyyar yin hakan da kyau kuma an yi ta daɗaɗaɗa, tana tuna da talabijin na yara.
Ba komai ne na asali ba.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ina tambayar kaina, shin, a yanzu, masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya tunanin wani rawar da za ta girmama baiwar Rowan Atkinson ba?
Labour ta musanta cewa jam'iyyar ta na shirin samar da tsarin da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma su samu albashi na kwana biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn ta yi la'akari da shirin da zai sa Britaniyawa su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma su samu albashi na kwana biyar.
An ce jam'iyyar ta so shugabannin kamfanoni su ba da ma'aikatan su ƙarin hutu na kwana ɗaya don samun ceton da suka samu daga juyin juya halin Artificial Intelligence (AI).
Hakan yana ba ma'aikata damar yin amfani da ƙarshen mako na kwana uku, amma har ila suna samun kuɗin da suka dace.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi ya dace da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ake yi na mayar da ma'aunin kasar zuwa ga ma'aikata.
An riga an amince da sauye-sauyen zuwa mako na aiki na kwana huɗu a cikin ƙungiyar kungiyoyin sana'a, wanda ya yi imanin cewa yana da kyau a tabbatar da cewa ma'aikata suna amfana daga yanayin tattalin arziki da ke canjawa.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sake fasalin manufofinsa kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba za a yi hakan ba a kowane lokaci, amma mako na aiki na kwana huɗu ya dace da manufar jam'iyyar ta ƙara inganta tattalin arzikin da ke amfanar ma'aikata kuma ya dace da tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce jam'iyyar farko da ta goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, ganin cewa jam'iyyar Green ta riga ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a makon zaben kasar na 2017.
Amma a halin yanzu, duk jam'iyyar Labour ba ta goyon bayan wannan burin ba.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Yakin aiki na kwana huɗu ba manufar jam'iyyar ba ce kuma jam'iyyar ba ta yin la'akari da shi".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron Labour a makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar karbar ikon "masu-fasahar da ba su da fuska" da "masu-samun riba" a kamfanonin da ke amfani da kayayyaki.
Shadow Chancellor's plans kuma na nufin cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu na ruwa bazai iya samun cikakken darajar hannun jari ba, saboda gwamnatin Labour za ta iya amfani da 'yancin' bisa ga rashin adalci da aka lura.
Ya kuma tabbatar da cewa akwai shirye-shiryen shigar da ma'aikata a cikin kwamitin gudanarwa na kamfanoni da kuma kafa Asusun Mallaka na Kasuwanci (Inclusive Ownership Funds) wanda zai ba da kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari na kamfanoni na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata da za su iya samun har zuwa £500 a shekara.
