Mene ne bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma shin ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar da ta gabata ne za a shirya bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke nuna wasu taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma da manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A karo na bakwai, dubban mutane za su halarci bikin Global Citizen Festival a Great Lawn na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin dadin irin waɗannan abubuwa kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar: kawar da talauci ta hanyar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara shirya a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, kungiyar masu fafutukar kare hakkin kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da ta.
Masu halartar taro da suke son samun tikitin kyauta don taron (sai dai idan sun yarda su biya kuɗin tikitin VIP), suna bukatar su kammala wasu ayyuka, ko 'ayyukan' kamar su yin aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin hira ta waya, ko kuma yin wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar: kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya aka samu nasarar gudanar da bikin Global Citizen Festival, da kuma ci gaba da shekaru 12 don cimma wannan burin?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ta kyauta hanya ce mai kyau don shawo kan mutane su nemi kira zuwa aiki ko kuma wani nau'i ne na "clicktivism", sa mutane su ji cewa suna ba da gudummawa ta hanyar sanya hannu kan wata takarda ta yanar gizo ko kuma aikawa da tweet?
Tun daga shekara ta 2011, a cewar Global Citizen, an yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan magoya baya, wadanda suka shafi dalilai daban-daban.
A cewar Global Citizen, waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su yi aiki da kuma gabatar da manufofi masu darajar fiye da dala biliyan 37 da za su iya canja rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 kafin shekara ta 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci ayyukan da aka yi da kuma sanarwa 390 da aka yi dangane da ayyukan, wanda aƙalla an biya dala biliyan 10 ko kuma aka tara ta hanyar tallafawa.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Babban sanarwa na nufin da aka yi shi ne na The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu gudanarwa daga Birtaniya da ke neman 'taimaka yara su cika iyakar abin da suke da shi.'
