Washington DC da jihohi 18 sun goyi bayan zanga-zangar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma District of Columbia sun goyi bayan zanga-zangar doka kan sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana mafaka ga wadanda ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali na 'yan bindiga ko kuma na gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da Washington D.C. sun gabatar da wata sanarwa a kotun Washington a ranar Juma'a a matsayin "abokin kotu" don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke jayayya da wannan manufar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar 'yancin bil'adama ta Amurka ta shigar da kara a watan Agusta ba.
Ta ce mijinta "da kuma 'ya'yansa maza masu aikata mugunta da suke cikin 'yan bindiga" sun yi mata fyade amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi takardar neman mafaka ta ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas bayan haka.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, inda yawancin mutanen da ke neman mafaka a Amurka suka fito, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fama da manyan matsalolin 'yan bindiga da tashin hankali a gida.
Sabon manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta yi watsi da wani hukunci na 2014 na Hukumar Kula da Kararrakin Baƙi, wanda ya ba da damar baƙi marasa takaddun da ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali na gida su nemi mafaka.
A wata sanarwa da aka yi a ranar Juma'a, babban mai gabatar da kara na Washington, D.C., Karl Racine ya ce sabon manufar "ta yi watsi da dokokin jihohi, na tarayya da na ƙasashen duniya na shekaru da yawa".
"Hukumar tarayya ta bukaci a yi la'akari da duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga ainihin abubuwan da ake yi da kuma yanayin da ake ciki, kuma irin wannan hanawa ya saba wa wannan ka'idar", in ji bayanin 'abokin kotu.'
Masu ba da shawara sun ci gaba da jayayya cewa manufar hana 'yan gudun hijira shiga Amurka tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, saboda waɗannan 'yan gudun hijira suna iya zama sababbin' yan kasuwa kuma suna ba da ƙasar 'ma'aikata da ake buƙata.'
A watan Yuni, ministan shari'a Jeff Sessions ya ba da umarnin cewa a daina ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka sha wahala daga tashin hankali a gida da kuma gangs.
"Ana samun mafaka ga waɗanda suka tsere daga ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro bisa ga launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko kasancewa cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa yin nufin cewa mafaka ba ce ta magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana, ko'ina cikin duniya, ko da kuwa suna da tsanani.
