Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi yana shirin samar da wani sabon intanet don ya mamaye Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya fara wani kamfani da ke neman yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt, sabuwar aikin da aka yi a tarihin fasaha, wani kamfani ne wanda aka kafa bisa dandamali na Open Source Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wane mutum ne ke samun damar yin amfani da wane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa "mulkin duniya" shi ne babban ra'ayin Inrupt.
"Ya kamata mu yi haka yanzu", ya ce game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar yin nasu 'takarar bayanan kan layi' ko POD.
Za a iya ajiye jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan, kalandar aiki, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da kuma wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa tare ta hanyar burauzar guda kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa POD ya zama na musamman shi ne cewa ya dogara da mai amfani da shi wanda ke samun damar yin amfani da wane bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Babban daraktan kamfanin, John Bruce, ya ce manufar Inrupt ita ce, kamfanin zai samar da albarkatu, matakai da kuma basira da ake bukata don samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi wa kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye.
Daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya yin aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da "Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji wanda zai sa dukkanin tsarin kasuwancin su su zama cikakke a lokaci guda".
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A wani rubutu da aka wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "manufin (Inrupt) shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo, wanda aka gina akan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Bayan Inrupt ta fara aiki, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
