Ronaldo ya musanta zargin da ake masa na fyade yayin da lauyoyinsa ke shirin kai karar wata mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya bayyana zargin da ake masa na yin hakan a matsayin "labari na karya" kuma ya ce mutane suna "son su tallata kansu" ta hanyar amfani da sunansa.
Lauyoyinsa suna shirin shigar da karar a jaridar Der Spiegel, wadda ta wallafa zargin.
An zargi dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da harbi da ya kai wa wata mata 'yar Amurka mai suna Kathryn Mayorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An kuma zarge shi da biyan ta dala 375,000 don ta yi shiru game da lamarin, jaridar Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
A wani bidiyo da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Instagram Live, wanda ke da mabiya miliyan 142 a duniya, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya bayyana cewa, 'yan sa'o'i bayan da aka yi rahoton zargin, rahoton ya zama 'haɗari marasa kyau'.
"A'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, a'a.
Abin da suke faɗa a yau, labarai ne na karya", in ji wanda ya lashe kyautar Ballon d'Or biyar a kan kamara.
"Suna son su yi wa kansu wa'azi ta wajen kiran sunana.
Hakan na al'ada ne.
Suna son su zama sanannu ta wurin furta sunana, amma hakan wani ɓangare ne na sana'a.
Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki, kuma ina yin hakan da kyau".
Lauyoyin Ronaldo suna shirin shigar da kara a gaban kotu domin su gurfanar da Der Spiegel bisa zargin da suka kira "rashin yarda da rahoto game da zargin sirri", in ji Reuters.
Lauya Christian Schertz ya ce dan wasan yana son a biya shi "damar da ya yi wa mutanensa laifin da ya dace da tsanani da ya yi, wanda wataƙila ya fi tsanani a cikin laifin da ya shafi hakkin mutum a cikin 'yan shekarun nan".
An ce wannan lamarin ya faru ne a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009 a wani dakunan shakatawa na Palms Hotel and Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a wani gidan wasan dare, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma dakin dan wasan, inda ake zargin ya yi mata fyade ta hanyar lalata, kamar yadda aka ruwaito a karar da aka shigar a Kotun Yankin Clark County, Nevada.
Mayorga ta ce bayan da aka yi zargin cewa Ronaldo ya yi rauni, ya gaya mata cewa "kashi 99" na mutumin kirki ne, amma wani lokacin ana watsi da shi.
Takardun sun ce Ronaldo ya tabbatar da cewa ma'aurata sun yi jima'i, amma hakan ya kasance da yardar juna.
Mayorga ta kuma ce ta je 'yan sanda kuma an dauki hotunan raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga baya ta amince da dokar hana fita domin tana "tsoron sakamakon" kuma tana damuwa da "yancin jama'a".
Yanzu, mai shekara 34 ya ce yana son a soke dokar domin an yi masa mummunan rauni a wani abu da ake zargin ya faru.
Ronaldo yana shirin komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United a lokacin da ake zargin an kai harin, kuma ya bar Juventus a Italiya a wannan bazarar a kan yarjejeniyar da ta kai dala miliyan 100.
Brexit: Birtaniya za ta yi nadama har abada idan masana'antun mota suka bar
Ministan tattalin arziki Greg Clark ya ce, Birtaniya za ta "yi nadama har abada" idan ta rasa matsayinta na jagora a duniya a fannin samar da motoci bayan Brexit.
Ya kara da cewa, "yana da damuwa" cewa Toyota UK ta gaya wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, kamfanin zai dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a cikin masana'antar a Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
Clark ya ce: "Muna bukatar mu yi yarjejeniya.
Kamfanin na samar da motocin kasar Japan ya ce sakamakon jinkirin da ake samu a kan iyakar kasar zai jawo rashin aikin yi idan aka yi yarjejeniya ta 'Brexit'.
A shekarar da ta gabata, masana'antar da ke Burnaston, inda ake kera Toyota's Auris da Avensis, ta samar da motoci kusan 150,000, kuma an fitar da kashi 90 cikin 100 daga cikinsu zuwa wasu ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai.
Marvin Cooke, manajan kamfanin Toyota a Burnaston, ya ce: "A ganina, idan Birtaniya ta bar EU a karshen watan Maris, za mu ga masana'antunmu sun daina aiki.
Wasu masana'antun kera motoci a Burtaniya, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover, sun bayyana damuwarsu game da sakamakon barin EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba ga ayyukan kasuwancin kan iyakoki.
Alal misali, BMW ta riga ta sanar da cewa za ta rufe masana'antar Mini a Oxford na wata ɗaya bayan Brexit.
Mafi yawan damuwa ga masana'antun mota game da hadarin da ke cikin sarkar samarwa idan akwai 'Brexit ba tare da yarjejeniya ba'.
Aikin Toyota na aiki ne bisa ka'idar 'just-in-time' inda kowane minti 37 kayayyakin gyara ke zuwa daga masu samar da motoci da aka yi wa oda a Birtaniya da kuma EU.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga Maris, za a iya samun tashin hankali a kan iyakoki wanda masana'antun ke ganin zai iya haifar da jinkiri da karancin kayayyaki.
Toyota ta sanar da cewa ba za ta iya ajiye kayayyaki ba fiye da rana ɗaya a cikin masana'antar Derbyshire, don haka a wannan yanayin za a dakatar da samarwa.
Clark ya ce shirin Chequers na Theresa May na dangantakar ta da EU a nan gaba "yana da daidai don kauce wa waɗannan dubawa a kan iyaka".
"Dole ne mu yi yarjejeniya, muna son mafi kyawun yarjejeniya, wanda zai ba mu damar ci gaba da nasarar da muke da ita a yanzu, amma kuma mu yi amfani da wannan damar", ya gaya wa masu sauraron shirin BBC Radio 4 na yau.
"Hakika, ba kawai daga Toyota ba, har ma daga wasu masana'antun, muna bukatar mu ci gaba da yin amfani da waɗannan jerin jerin jerin hanyoyin samar da kayayyaki masu nasara".
Toyota ba ta iya faɗi tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samarwa ba, amma ta yi gargadin cewa a cikin dogon lokaci ƙarin farashin zai shafi matsayin gasa na kamfanin kuma hakan zai haifar da asarar ayyukan yi.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston na shekaru 24 kuma shi ne wakilin ƙungiyar Unite a wurin aiki, ya ce, 'yan'uwansa suna ƙara damuwa: "A cikin kwarewata, idan an rasa waɗannan ayyukan, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
Wani kakakin gwamnatin ya ce: "Mun gabatar da wani tsari mai kyau da kuma abin dogaro ga dangantakarmu da EU a nan gaba".
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce za a iya jinkirta taron Trump da Rosenstein
Babban taron da Donald Trump ya yi da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya "karbar wani mako" yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein na kula da aikin da mai gabatar da kara na musamman Robert Mueller ya yi, wanda ke bincike kan tasirin Rasha a zaben, alaƙar da ke tsakanin mataimakan Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban ya shiga kotu.
Tambayar ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya, wanda hakan zai sa 'yancin kai na Mueller ya kasance cikin haɗari, ta shafe watanni tana ta tayar da hankalin Washington.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna yiwuwar saka makirufo don yin rikodin tattaunawa da Trump da kuma sa shugaban kasa ya yi murabus ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta shige, sa'ad da ya je fadar White House, jita-jita sun yi ta cewa zai yi murabus.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da cewa za a yi taro da Trump, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a birnin New York, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce bai so ya kori Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka yi watsi da taron don kauce wa rikici da za a yi da Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa, inda Kavanaugh da ɗaya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da lalata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, za su yi shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba FBI umarni ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya sa aka sake jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa.
A ranar Lahadi, Sarah Sanders, shugaban yada labarai na Trump ta fito a tashar talabijin ta Fox News.
Da aka tambaye ta game da taron da ta yi da Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an ba da kwanan wata ba, zai iya zama wannan makon, amma kuma za a iya jinkirta shi na wata mako, saboda duk sauran abubuwan da ke gudana a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu ga, kuma ina son in sanar da manema labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi kokawa da wannan ikirarin: Sanders bai yi taron manema labarai a fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga Satumba.
Mai masaukin gayyata Chris Wallace ya tambaye ta dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta ce rashin taron manema labarai ba don ƙiyayya da 'yan jaridar TV masu jan hankali ba ne, ko da yake ta kara da cewa: "Ba zan musanta cewa suna kokarin jawo hankali ba".
Ta kuma ce za a samu karin sadarwa tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
"Shugaban kasa ya yi tambayoyi da amsoshi fiye da kowane shugaban kasa a gabansa", in ji ta, ba tare da ta ba da hujja ba. "Mun duba alkaluman".
Sanders ya ce za a ci gaba da yin taron manema labarai, amma "idan manema labarai sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, hakan ya fi magana da ni kyau.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai kuma kun ga muna yin hakan sau da yawa a cikin makonnin da suka gabata kuma hakan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai idan kun iya magana da shugaban Amurka".
Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a kai a kai a lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma lokacin da ya halarci taron jama'a ko kuma yayin taron manema labarai da manyan mutane da ke ziyartar.
Ba a yawan yin taron manema labarai da shugaban kasa kaɗai ba.
A birnin New York a wannan makon, shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa ya yi wa 'yan jarida da suka taru a taron wani bayyanar da ba ta dace ba.
Ministan kiwon lafiya ya rubuta wasiƙa game da Brexit ga ma'aikatan NHS Scotland daga wasu ƙasashen EU
Ministan kiwon lafiya ya rubuta wasiƙa ga ma'aikatan EU da ke aiki a NHS Scotland don nuna godiyar ƙasar da kuma fatan su ci gaba da aiki a NHS bayan Brexit.
Jeane Freeman, MSP, ta aika da wata wasiƙa da ta rage watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta amince ta ɗauki nauyin biyan kuɗin neman matsayin dangi na dindindin ga 'yan ƙasar EU da ke aiki a ayyukan gwamnati na gari.
A cikin wasiƙarta, Freeman ta rubuta: "A lokacin rani, tattaunawar tsakanin Birtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, kuma za a yanke shawarar da ake tsammani a wannan kaka.
Amma a lokaci guda, gwamnatin Burtaniya ta yi shiri sosai don yiwuwar rashin cimma yarjejeniya.
Na san cewa waɗannan lokatai ne masu wuya a gare ku duka.
Saboda haka, ina so in sake nuna yadda nake godiya ga gudummawar da dukan ma'aikatanmu suke bayarwa, ko da wane irin ƙasa suke.
Abokan aiki daga ko'ina cikin EU da wajen suna kawo kwarewa da ƙwarewa masu tamani waɗanda ke ƙarfafa da kuma inganta ayyukan NHS kuma suna ba da fa'idodi ga marasa lafiya da al'ummomin da muke bauta wa.
Hakika, Scotland gida ce a gare ku, kuma muna son ku zauna a nan".
