Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu za su ci gaba da ƙaruwa.
Saboda an kashe hanyoyin sadarwa, hukumomin ba su samu wani bayani ba daga yankin Donggala, yankin da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da wurin da girgizar ƙasa ta yi da ƙarfin 7.5 a sikelin Richter.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Middle Celebes ne kuma yana kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Celebes, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da tsunami ya auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai tsawon kilomita 300 a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Celebes.
A shekara ta 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin da ke ƙarƙashin lardin.
Fishing da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arzikin lardin Midden Celebes, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana amfani da ma'adinai na nickel a lardin, amma mafi yawan su suna Morowali, a bakin tekun Celebes.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya shafi Palu da Donggala, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekarar 1996, tsunami ya afku a yammacin Donggala kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa sau da yawa.
Ga jerin wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin tekun lardin Atjeh na arewacin Sumatra a Indonesiya a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Atjeh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 6.8 a sikelin Richter ta faru a kudancin Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar kudu da kusan 700 da ke mutuwa.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 a sikelin Richter ta afkawa garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin sikelin Richter 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayi fiye da mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani mummunan girgizar ƙasa ya afkawa gwamnatin Pidie a Atjeh, ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici, saboda an tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan karon babu tsunami amma mutane fiye da 100 ne suka mutu sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa da yawa ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda aka kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido su yi sanyin gwiwa.
An kama ɗansa na farko da ake zargi da aikata mugunta a gida
Track Palin, babban dan Sarah Palin, tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, an kama shi bisa zargin yin lalata a gida.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29 a Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin yin ta'addanci a gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton ta'addanci a gida, da kuma yin tsayayya a lokacin da ake tuhuma, a cewar wani rahoto da Alaska State Troopers ta saki a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, sa'ad da wata mace da ya san ta ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kawo rahoton laifin da ake zargi, ya karɓi wayar ta.
An tsare Palin a gidan tsare Mat-Su a kan bashin dala 500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar kuma ya bayyana kansa "mara laifi, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi wannan, cibiyar sadarwar ta ruwaito.
Ana tuhumar Palin da laifin aikata laifuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin aji na B, wanda zai iya kai ga kurkuku na kwana daya da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Ba wannan ne karon farko da ake tuhumar Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da zaluntar mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
A lokacin ne mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su gaya mata cewa an yi mata fyade.
Wannan shari'ar ta yi aiki a gaban Kotun Tsoffin Sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton tashin hankali na gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin abin da ya faru.
Abokinsa ta ce ya bugi ta a fuska.
A shekarar 2016, wata ƙungiyar tsoffin sojoji ta soki Sarah Palin bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankali na ɗanta da PTSD, wanda ya ce ya sa ya yi aiki a Iraki.
