Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yi wa wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York kisa mai wuya
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York sun bukaci a yanke wa Sajfoello Sajpov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da aka kai a birnin New York, inda aka kashe mutane takwas, wanda ba a yi kisa a jihar ba tun 1953.
An zargi Sajpov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da wata babbar motar haya daga Home Depot don ya kai hari a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke da suka zo a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Sajpov ya kashe wadanda suka mutu takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni, a cewar takardar da ke neman hukuncin kisa, wadda aka gabatar a Kananan Hukumomin New York.
A kan waɗannan tuhuma biyu, an ba da hukuncin kisa, in ji takardar da aka gabatar a gaban kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta amince da tuhumar da aka yi mata da tuhuma 22, ciki har da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai don amfani da racket, wanda ya saba da tuhumar da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da ita wajen magance aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar da ake yi wa mutane da suka aikata mugunta da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da shiri mai zurfi", kuma sun bayyana yadda Sajpov ya yi harin a matsayin "m, da zalunci, da kuma lalata".
"Sajfoello Habiboellayevich Sajpov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da asarar rayuka", in ji sanarwar.
