A shekarar 1953, an yi wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a birnin New York, bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka shige saboda yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yaƙin Tsakiya.
